    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155320/extras/7706a5b3b3bb41cdbb7076b58cecade1.avif?t=1747665117\" width=800 height=205 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Athos BlackThorne is the lord of the castle but this may be his last day. Caught between the accusations of the Church, the claims of the Empire and the resistance of the indigenous peoples of the BlackForest, he will fall into a web of conspiracy, treason and deceit that seeks to replace him as the ruling power in the region. His last resort is turning to a cursed artifact that saved his family several times in the past - but at what cost? With this power in hand, Athos must face a series of tragical events, navigating his choices, allies and foes to figure out how to survive what may be the last dawn of the BlackThorne Keep. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ENGAGING DELIBERATE DIRECTIONAL COMBAT</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155320/extras/3e37bb870e77ac442c762cff74250e06.poster.avif?t=1747665117\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155320/extras/3e37bb870e77ac442c762cff74250e06.webm?t=1747665117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155320/extras/3e37bb870e77ac442c762cff74250e06.mp4?t=1747665117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Combat is paced, deliberate and mortally strategical - Your Mastery will be tested!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXPLORE A BRAND NEW MEDIEVAL WORLD</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155320/extras/68900b3c06bb6dafaa7b9f33709834a1.poster.avif?t=1747665117\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155320/extras/68900b3c06bb6dafaa7b9f33709834a1.webm?t=1747665117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155320/extras/68900b3c06bb6dafaa7b9f33709834a1.mp4?t=1747665117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Dozens of locations and secrets to discover and explore</i></strong><br>The World of Paragonia is based on a low fantasy tabletop RPG that takes place in a world that imagines how a medieval colonial era would be.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SOLVE INSTIGATING PUZZLES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155320/extras/29e2a027d1ec566ec486ae207b247a5b.poster.avif?t=1747665117\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155320/extras/29e2a027d1ec566ec486ae207b247a5b.webm?t=1747665117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155320/extras/29e2a027d1ec566ec486ae207b247a5b.mp4?t=1747665117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Solve mysteries within  Ancient Ruins and Sherathian cities.</strong></i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BUILT WITH PASSION</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155320/extras/7afbbefbe1241981a0959d8dce8df3ef.poster.avif?t=1747665117\" width=498 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155320/extras/7afbbefbe1241981a0959d8dce8df3ef.webm?t=1747665117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155320/extras/7afbbefbe1241981a0959d8dce8df3ef.mp4?t=1747665117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Started by a single Developer, 20 years in the making.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Based on the BlackThorne Keep tabletop RPG and on the exploits of the BlackThorne Keep gaming community, this is the culmination of 20 years of gaming across multiple medias. A homage to two decades of gathered stories and friends. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155320/extras/18dd3ec668130f45b882deb7a7cec5a7.webp?t=1747665117\" width=581 height=46 /></span></p>",
